cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper is about image-to-image translation using GANs and novel regularizers. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also introduces a new architecture and explores new regularizers, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves optimization and regularization techniques, which could place it in cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
